# Workflow 10 — AI Email Auto Responder
## AI Automation Freelancer Training — June 2026

---

## What This Workflow Does

Someone sends an email to a business Gmail account.
n8n catches it within 1 minute.
AI reads the email and understands what the person wants.
AI writes a professional human-sounding reply automatically.
The reply gets sent back to the sender instantly.
Everything gets logged to Google Sheets for tracking.
The business owner never has to touch routine emails again.

---

## Tools I Used

```
Gmail         → Catch incoming emails and send replies
n8n           → Run the entire automation
OpenAI        → Read emails and write replies
Google Sheets → Log every email and response
```

---

## Full Workflow Flow

```
Someone sends an email to Gmail
            ↓
01 - Watch Incoming Email
     Checks inbox every 1 minute
     Fires when new email arrives
            ↓
02 - Extract Email Data
     Pulls out sender name, sender email,
     subject, and body cleanly
            ↓
03 - AI Read and Reply
     Sends email data to GPT-4o-mini
     AI reads it and writes a professional reply
            ↓
04 - Parse AI Response
     Extracts reply and category from AI text
     Combines everything into one clean output
            ↓
05 - Send Reply
     Sends AI written reply back to sender via Gmail
            ↓
06 - Log to Sheet
     Saves sender, subject, body, reply, timestamp
     to Google Sheets for full tracking
```

---

---

