Headers in Row 1:
A1: Timestamp
B1: Sender Name
C1: Sender Email
D1: Subject
E1: Email Body
F1: AI Reply
G1: Status
```

## n8n Setup
```
Open n8n
New Workflow
Name it: Workflow 10 - AI Email Auto Responder
```

## Why I Planned First
Experts never open n8n and start clicking randomly.
I know what I am building before I build it.
Sheet headers match exactly what the workflow will produce.
No surprises. No rework.

