# Quick Node Reference

```
01 - Watch Incoming Email
     Gmail Trigger — On message received
     Poll: Every 1 Minute

02 - Extract Email Data
     Edit Fields (Set) — Manual Mapping
     Fields: sender_email, sender_name, subject, body
     Body uses: $json.snippet

03 - AI Read and Reply
     OpenAI — GPT-4o-mini
     System Prompt with 4 email type templates
     Returns JSON: reply + category

04 - Parse AI Response
     Code Node — JavaScript
     Path: output[0].content[0].text
     Combines Node 02 data + AI output

05 - Send Reply
     Gmail — Send Email
     To: sender_email
     Subject: Re: + subject
     Body: AI reply

06 - Log to Sheet
     Google Sheets — Append Row
     Logs everything + Status: Replied
     Uses $('04 - Parse AI Response').item.json.xxx
```

